NAME
    GrowthForecast - Lightning Fast Graphing/Visualization

        for Heroku using MySQL and Amazon S3

SYNOPSIS
      % heroku create --stack cedar --buildpack http://github.com/riywo/heroku-buildpack-perl.git
      % heroku addons:add xeround:starter
      % heroku config:add S3_KEY=XXXXXXXXXXX
      % heroku config:add S3_SECRET=YYYYYYYYYYYY
      % heroku config:add S3_BUCKET=yourbucket
      % heroku config:add MYSQL_USER=user
      % heroku config:add MYSQL_PASSWORD=password
      % heroku config:add MYSQL_DSN="dbi:mysql:DBNAME;hostname=DNS:PORT"
      % git push heroku heroku-s3:master

DESCRIPTION
    GrowthForecast is graphing/visualization web tool built on RRDtool

    This branch is for Heroku.

